    <title>Fairness for Our Hospitals Act of 2017</title>
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <actionDate>2017-04-27</actionDate>
          <updateDate>2017-04-27T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Fairness for Our Hospitals Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to allow a hospital that meets specified criteria and is located in a state with no rural areas to be considered a Medicare-dependent hospital. The Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services shall establish and implement a process for reimbursing impacted hospitals for any underpayments resulting from this bill's implementation.</p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-07-17T17:57:04Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
